322
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:40,400
Are you not used to it?

323
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:45,000
Sports marketing is a part of an athlete's job.

324
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:47,200
Look at all your fans online.

325
00:17:47,200 --> 00:17:48,900
If they got more interested in sports

326
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:50,500
after watching your commercial,

327
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:53,400
that'd be a good thing, right?

328
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:55,600
All right, don't overthink it.

329
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:58,600
