Just like I told you yesterday.

341
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,600
This is the feeling you want.

342
00:18:24,700 --> 00:18:26,400
Okay, be more determined.

343
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:28,700
Give me a tougher gaze.

344
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:30,300
Okay!

345
00:18:30,300 --> 00:18:31,000
Don't worry.

346
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,400
We've booked a hotel for you all

347
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:34,000
