348
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,700
"Hotel"?

349
00:18:35,700 --> 00:18:37,100
We need to...

350
00:18:37,100 --> 00:18:38,800
Stay here one night.

351
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:43,300
