397
00:20:42,200 --> 00:20:44,000
Just one bite. It's really, really good!

398
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,700
- I don't want any.
- Try it!

399
00:20:45,700 --> 00:20:47,900
I don't want any. I really don't.

400
00:20:47,900 --> 00:20:49,800
You're quite self-aware.

401
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:50,900
I can't.

