403
00:20:54,600 --> 00:20:56,200
You have a bright future, Young Man.

404
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:58,000
Of course.

405
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,800
Let's check this out.

406
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:01,500
