00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:05,500
These are exclusive designs.

409
00:21:05,500 --> 00:21:07,700
I want to choose one.

410
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:09,400
Two minutes,

411
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:10,600
