412
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,600
Okay.

413
00:21:11,600 --> 00:21:13,800
Give me the fries; I'll hold them.

414
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,400
Which one is prettier?

415
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:22,600
They all look pretty on you.

