00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:33,800
This is an exclusive design.

417
00:21:33,800 --> 00:21:35,300
You can't buy it elsewhere.

418
00:21:35,300 --> 00:21:37,100
I'll take it.

419
00:21:37,100 --> 00:21:38,500
Okay.

420
00:21:39,600 --> 00:21:41,400
These are all from the internet.

421
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:43,700
She'll make half the price as profit.

422
00:21:43,700 --> 00:21:46,000
But she said you can't buy it elsewhere.

423
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,600
Why are you so gullible?

424
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:50,800
How about I give you a discount of 30% off for two pairs?

425
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:53,200
We'll take them.

426
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:56,200
I'll take one of both pairs she tried on. Here's two hundred ($30) total.

427
00:21:56,200 --> 00:21:58,600
- Does that work?
- Yes.

428
00:21:58,600 --> 00:22:00,200
The payment went through.

429
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,100
Don't move.

430
00:22:02,100 --> 00:22:03,500
Let me.

431
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:06,200
Give it to me.

432
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:56,600
Done.

433
00:22:57,600 --> 00:22:59,600
Did it hurt?

434
00:22:59,600 --> 00:23:01,000
Does it look good?

435
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:03,500
It's one of a kind; of course, it looks good.

436
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:05,400
Let's go.

437
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:06,700
Let's go.

438
00:23:06,700 --> 00:23:07,700
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

439
00:23:07,700 --> 00:23:09,200
You're welcome.

440
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:11,600
- Give it to me.
- No.

441
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:13,700
You need to stop eating.

