The Diamond League high jump finals.

443
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,800
Impressive.

444
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:28,000
I know this athlete.

445
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,500
He just debuted last year

446
00:23:29,500 --> 00:23:31,300
