447
00:23:31,300 --> 00:23:33,200
He's so good.

448
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:37,500
Let's go.

449
00:23:39,100 --> 00:23:40,600
Let's go.

450
00:23:51,500 --> 00:23:53,000
Come on.

451
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:55,200
Good night.

452
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:57,000
Wh-What do you mean?

453
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,200
Aren't you coming up?

454
00:23:58,200 --> 00:23:59,400
I can't go up.

455
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:00,500
What do you mean?

456
00:24:00,500 --> 00:24:02,600
You came all the way here. Let's go.

457
00:24:02,600 --> 00:24:04,800
