458
00:24:04,800 --> 00:24:05,800
You're being naughty. Come here.

459
00:24:05,800 --> 00:24:07,000
- Listen to me.
- You can if I say so.

460
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:08,800
- Be good now!
- I don't want to.

461
00:24:08,800 --> 00:24:10,900
Just go to sleep.

462
00:24:11,600 --> 00:24:12,700
All right, be good now.

463
00:24:12,700 --> 00:24:14,000
But why?

464
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:17,200
You came all the way here. Why aren't you coming up?

465
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:20,600
