498
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:54,100
especially me.

499
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:58,200
Then you must work hard.

500
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:01,100
Don't let anything distract you.

501
00:26:01,100 --> 00:26:02,800
Got it?

502
00:26:07,300 --> 00:26:10,500
Two weeks are left until Asian Athletics Championships.

503
00:26:10,500 --> 00:26:12,700
